menu "Applications & tasking"
  choice
  prompt "Tasking model"
  
  config TASKING_FLAT
  bool "Flat tasking model"
  help
   In the flat tasking model all ANTARES_APP macros glue application code one by one
   in one huge loop (Unless any application blocks that with an endless loop.
   Priority settings are ignored, if any.

  config TASKING_MULTI
  bool "Antares Multi-tasking kernel (EXPERIMENTAL)"
    help
    In the multi-tasking model all the code from ANTARES_APP become separate threads. 
    
  endchoice

source "src/apps/kcnf"

endmenu

